{"tid":507854,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★狂賀！限制舊IPhone性能 US用戶集體起訴Apple！","createTime":"2017-12-23T16:09:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-24T14:04:05.000Z","uid":19454,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"47dc38daadc864a69b8ce3a130c5ff211bec952a","tid":507854,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T16:09:07.000Z","msg":"在今個星期三，蘋果承認限制舊iPhone的性能，原因是避免手機因如發生電量耗盡而自動關機。就在日前，<span style=\"color: red;\">美國洛杉磯iPhone用家Stefan Bodganovich，就因這種解釋而向蘋果提出集體訴訟</span>。受影響的舊款機型包括iPhone 6、iPhone 6s 、iPhone SE，甚至上一代的iPhone 7。而向起訴蘋果的用戶Stefan，就是iPhone 7的用家<br />\n<br />\n受害人Stefan表示不認同蘋果做法，並認為這手段損害iPhone價值，蘋果旨在讓用戶買新機。其更稱iPhone用家從未要求蘋果降低舊款手機的性能，以節省電量。同時，他要求蘋果停止限制老款iPhone性能的做法，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">並作出賠償。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://pc3mag.com/apple-slow-old-iphone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpc3mag.com%2Fapple-slow-old-iphone%2F&d=YOYowMKT4GHpmLnXTDE8Rv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=9bcf9b2f\" target=\"_blank\">http://pc3mag.com/apple-slow-old-iphone/</a>"},{"pid":"da9bd79f6c2435b73aaa217822a194c37645dda3","tid":507854,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T16:09:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25428396b2611f296c54ae28444c990fc86188a9","tid":507854,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T16:10:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>破產！<br />\n破產！<br />\n破產！<br />\n破產！</strong></span>"},{"pid":"69f623772b3cd4553d3687dfa7578aa422392744","tid":507854,"uid":53429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T16:10:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有老貓就預左